# Domain module confirmation page (DOMAIN_MODULE_CHECKLIST.md)

Chinese locale: [`domain-module-checklist.zh-CN.md`](./domain-module-checklist.zh-CN.md).

**When**: Editing or refreshing `domain-knowledge/curated/by-root/<root>/DOMAIN_MODULE_CHECKLIST.md`; or right after **`@generate-knowledge-from-wiki`** / **`@distill-domain-knowledge`**.

**Layout**: `domain-knowledge/DOMAIN_MODULE_CHECKLIST.template.md` · **Full flow**: `.cursor/skills/generate-knowledge-from-wiki/RUNBOOK.md`

**Narrow layout (required)**: one block per theme — `### Theme name` + `- **Field**: value`. **Do not** write wide tables (`Theme | strategy | … | Status`). Humans usually only change **Status** (`pending` → `confirmed`). Locale status strings: `domain-knowledge/language/deliverable-locale-tokens.json`.

## 1. Yardstick

Use only `domain-knowledge/strategy.md` **§2** — **do not** invent a separate industry standard.

## 2. S2 (when refreshing this page)

- **Theme blocks** = `strategy.md` §2 × scan of `materialized/`
- **Tagging** = each `materialized/**/*.md` → `_materialization_closure.json`
- **Forbidden**: paste the same `materialized/` body into multiple output dirs
- **Scattered-source coverage**: full-text search + semantic gap-fill on `materialized/`; prior stable `glossary.md` is synonym/abbrev hints only, **not** domain-boundary authority. Write completed paths into closure and this page; new terms into **glossary note**; **do not** treat filenames or `facet-*` alone as covered
- **Pause**: wait for humans to set accepted modules' **Status** to **`confirmed`** — **only if** the row has tagged sources (Note must not say zero sources). Leave empty-evidence rows **pending**.
- On refresh, S2 rewrites **Note** from Status + source count (clears stale “awaiting human confirm” after confirm).

## 3. Deliver (user says **`continue`**)

Only **`confirmed`** modules: **S3** `_aggregate/` → **S4** domain model → **S5** work draft → **S6** source brief → **S7** locale brief.

## 4. Gates

- After S2 (recommended): `python3 scripts/distill/coverage.py --root-id <root>`
- After S7: `python3 scripts/domain_check.py distill --root-id <root>`

## 5. Appendix links on this page

`_materialization_closure.json`, `_appendix/` (if present).

## 6. Forbidden

- Invent business numbers or policies absent from Confluence; if unsure write “TBD” and keep provenance
- **S1–S5**: no translation
- Cite `materialized/` only as single-line refs under brief **`## Provenance`** (see `distill-quality-bar.md`)
- Reintroduce wide Markdown tables on this confirmation page
